{"tid":2224146,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美駐聯國大使︰沒有台灣的聯合國是自欺欺人、欺騙世界","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T11:58:40.000Z","uid":76710,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62eb160780e7c2244e24e3fa08cc04347d571ab5","tid":2224146,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲 中共快啲制裁美國大使 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USAmbUN/status/1311117110018535431?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAmbUN%2Fstatus%2F1311117110018535431%3Fs%3D20&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyvvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=a1da7114\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAmbUN%2Fstatus%2F1311117110018535431%3Fs%3D20&h=86a1c159\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USAmbUN/status/1311117110018535431?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3307701?fbclid=IwAR3NVtR_RwtzeLSEYOn7PozjMAzoAXsXsOvwTN_NblfQ_xbc3UJyach38hY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3307701%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3NVtR_RwtzeLSEYOn7PozjMAzoAXsXsOvwTN_NblfQ_xbc3UJyach38hY&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyvvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=78fb550b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3307701%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3NVtR_RwtzeLSEYOn7PozjMAzoAXsXsOvwTN_NblfQ_xbc3UJyach38hY&h=0722a2c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3307701?fbclid=IwAR3NVtR_RwtzeLSEYOn7PozjMAzoAXsXsOvwTN_NblfQ_xbc3UJyach38hY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020/09/30 12:18<br />\n〔記者呂伊萱／台北報導〕聯合國大會總辯論29日閉幕，本月中旬公開挺台重返聯合國的美國駐聯合國大使克拉夫特（Kelly Craft），29日參加活動致詞再次直言，台灣是良善力量，世界需要台灣「完整參與聯合國」，「沒有台灣的聯合國是自欺欺人、欺騙世界」。<br />\n<br />\n克拉夫特本月中旬與我駐紐約代表李光章餐敘，之後接受媒體訪問時稱這場與台灣官員的餐會是「歷史性會面」，並直言美國正在推動台灣重返聯合國。<br />\n<br />\n克拉夫特29日視訊出席台美日「全球合作暨訓練架構」（GCTF）框架下的「透過公私部門夥伴關係促進國際發展」活動，致詞時再次發表強力挺台訊息，克拉夫特也於推特公開轉發此篇致詞，推特照片背景中還出現台灣黑熊玩偶。<br />\n<br />\n克拉夫特談及，自2016年的「川蔡通話」開始，川普總統已經改變對中華人民共和國的態度，而聚集一起討論具體方法最能體現友誼，台灣和美國等夥伴為一個民主和更美好的世界而合作。<br />\n<br />\n克拉夫特說，世界需要台灣在聯合國的充分參與，尤其在公衛和經濟發展等事務上。台灣是世界良善力量，「缺少台灣充分參與的聯合國是自欺欺人、欺騙世界」。台灣在川普政府中有值得信賴的朋友，並持續支持台灣所扮演的國際角色，台灣理所應當在最重要的平台上擁有一席之地，以分享其卓越的創新和專業知識。"},{"pid":"3f7fec56a4b504ff583ce486286ee1fd91af5efb","tid":2224146,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"978462a88537ace0f7f6c6e8cd3a221f9ee1fcc7","tid":2224146,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d727a8f83d5c54eead78d5a7d6dd7b9c6bedeed","tid":2224146,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}